rded. Accordingly, <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4361537-marvell-technology-non-gaap-eps-of-0_43-beats-0_02-revenue-of-1_52b-beats-60m\">Marvell delivered a double beat</a> on revenue and adjusted EPS and also raised its guidance. The beat-and-raise</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1679337219/image_1679337219.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742053-marvell-q3-lofty-expectations-could-burn-investors-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:30:01"}, {"id": "4742071", "title": "Carbios: Reflexivity Risks With Limited Catalysts Until 2026", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"plastic garbage island\" data-id=\"1426542329\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">mbala mbala merlin</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Carbios SAS</strong> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COOSF\" title=\"Carbios SAS\">OTCPK:COOSF</a>, FR0011648716) has signed <a href=\"https://www.carbios.com/en/regulated-information/\" rel=\"nofollow\">another LOI apparently</a> in the UK, adding more potential income on top of the hoped for income discussed in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4717030-carbios-lois-signed-that-could-lead-to-licensing-deals\">our last article</a> from Turkey and China. There</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1426542329/image_1426542329.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742071-carbios-reflexivity-risks-with-limited-catalysts-until-2026", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:22:52"}, {"id": "4742069", "title": "Google: Chrome Divestiture Selloff Was A Gift For Investors", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Google office building in the Company\"s campus in Silicon Valley' data-id=\"1154834209\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5294px\" height=\"3529px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I had a 'Strong Buy' thesis on Google (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a></span>) in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723783-google-dont-miss-out-on-a-golden-discount\">September</a>. The stock did really well and outperformed the S&amp;P 500 until mid-November. However, the information regarding potential <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2024/nov/19/us-doj-sell-chrome-browser-ai-android\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Chrome divestiture</a> caused the stock price</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1154834209/image_1154834209.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742069-google-chrome-divestiture-selloff-was-a-gift-for-investors", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:14:26"}, {"id": "4742085", "title": "EUR/USD Hugs 1.0500 Ahead Of French No-Confidence Vote, Breakout Incoming?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Financial Stock Market Abstract Graph\" data-id=\"1370514197\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">koto_feja</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>The 1.0500 continues to serve as a magnet for EUR/USD with the pair moving higher or lower for brief periods before finding its way back to the psychological level. It appears market participants are waiting on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370514197/image_1370514197.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742085-eurusd-hugs-1-0500-ahead-of-french-no-confidence-vote-breakout-incoming", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 19:10:00"}, {"id": "4742066", "title": "LifeMD: A Story I Want A Small Piece Of", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman having online meeting with female healthcare person\" data-id=\"1224685401\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6720px\" height=\"4480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Solskin</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, we put <strong>LifeMD, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LFMD\" title=\"LifeMD, Inc.\">LFMD</a></span>)</strong> in the spotlight for the first time since March of this year. As can be seen below, the stock has been roughly cut in half from its recent highs in early May. The company is seeing impressive</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1224685401/image_1224685401.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742066-lifemd-lfmd-a-story-i-want-a-small-piece-of", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:57:32"}, {"id": "4742065", "title": "IAK: Trumpflation Keeps Reserve Portfolio Returns Higher", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Standing out from the Crowd concept 2\" data-id=\"1808744976\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The <strong>iShares U.S. Insurance ETF</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IAK\" title=\"iShares U.S. Insurance ETF\">IAK</a></span>) has been performing well against the market since <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4665638-iak-pricing-power-in-automotive\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4665638-iak-pricing-power-in-automotive\" target=\"_blank\">our last coverage</a>. We believe the conditions for performance are still in play. Correlation to financials is one factor, where Trump is positive</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808744976/image_1808744976.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742065-iak-trumpflation-keeps-reserve-portfolio-returns-higher", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:52:34"}, {"id": "4742061", "title": "Akatsuki: Remains A No-Brainer Into The End Of 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Capsule toy, gacha capsule, gacha gacha, etc.\" data-id=\"1368392148\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1017px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Kana Design Image /iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Akatsuki Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AKAFF\" title=\"Akatsuki Inc.\">OTCPK:AKAFF</a>), the primarily gacha game developer from Japan, reported earnings a few weeks ago, receiving a pretty clear thumbs up from markets after languishing once again for some months. Atelier Resleriana was released</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1368392148/image_1368392148.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742061-akatsuki-remains-a-no-brainer-into-the-end-of-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 18:40:09"}, {"id": "4742059", "title": "IGM Biosciences: Dizzying Number Of Pivots", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_imag